Ingredients
Jasmine rice
Garlic
Onion
Carrot
Beans
Egg
Salt
White pepper
Stock powder
Sugar
Soya sauce
Oyster sauce
Sesame oil





Method
Cook on high heat 

Sauté garlic and onions until well done

Add carrots and beans

Add eggs and scramble

Add cooked rice and mix well

Add salt, white pepper, stock powder, sugar, soya sauce, and oyster sauce

Add sesame oil





